title: Ableton Live - Sampled Instruments - EIC 2
description:
The Essential Instrument Collection 2 is a multi-gigabyte library of meticulously sampled and selected instruments created in cooperation with SONiVOX and ChocolateAudio. The Essential Instrument Collection 2 offers a choice selection of acoustic and electric pianos, guitars, bass, drums, orchestral strings, brass, woodwinds and more.

For Ableton Live (7+). More info: http://www.ableton.com/eic


........


NOTE: Apparently, this collection is incomplete. So far, it seems that there's probably a 'Drums.alp' missing from the set. If you happen to have it, please inform and make it available. 

Included packages:
Brass.alp
Choir.alp
EIC-LE.alp
GrandPiano.alp
Guitars.alp
Keys.alp
Percussion.alp
Strings.alp
Woodwinds.alp (w/ Ableton patch pre-applied)

I'd also suggest using an Ableton Live release by AiR, which bypasses the need for a product key (as i don't have one, myself).
